                <h2><a name="GoodNewsPersonalMessage"></a>Do you use your personal message to share good news with your contacts?</h2>
                    <p>Your personal message can be used to promote good news stories of recent work you have done.</p>
                    <p>If you have your <a href="RulesToBeingSoftwareConsultantsDealingWithClients.aspx#ClientsUsingMessenger">clients added as Instant Messenger contacts</a>, what better group of people to share good news with.</p>
                    <p>Your personal message should be simple, to the point, and make sure you change it at least once a month!</p>
