				    <p>When somebody sends you an email, they are not in fact interrupting you at all. You have made the decision to read your emails, so email is in actual fact far more polite than IM which is a complete nuisance.</p>
				    <p>IM is only to be used if they would like you to do something NOW.</p>
		    </li>

