                <h2><a name="ChatEfficient"></a>Do you make the communication more efficient by referring back to a subject of an email?</h2>
                    <p>Use IM to chase up that important email. You can make it easy for everyone (or at least give them the context of your questions) by pasting the email subject.</p>
                    <dl class="goodCode">
                        <dt>
                            <pre>I need you to reply to my email... <span style="background-color:Yellow">Subject: CBA Software Audit</span></pre>
